+++ Supernova Flare Scrap Vicyr Slasys +++

"Yes, sir," Supernova replied to Zardus when he recieved the order,
and then looked to his team. "We have permission to enter the IGL,"
he informed them, "but we need to meet a bot coming to the Iron Fist
first. Lets go."

Supernova turned and walked out of the holo-room along with his team
and headed for the exit of the Iron Fist. When they walked out of the
exit, they saw Daemos already flying in. Supernova looked in his
direction, and then narrowed his eyes as he looked at the coast of
Spain and saw an energon explosion.

"Vicyr, Slasys," he ordered, "Go check out that explosion. Me, Flare,
and Scrap will meet this new bot."

Vicyr and Slasys nodded and transformed. They combined into a jet and
flew off toward Wolfgang while Supernova, Flare, and Scrap used their
jetpacks to fly toward Daemos.

"Welcome to Alliance island." Said Supernova to Daemos over his comm
link. "My name is Supernova. Zardus sent me to escort you to him."



The jet that was Vicyr and Slasys landed near the stasis-locked
Wolfgang and seperated back into the individual bots. They both
approached him.

"Looks like he's out cold." Vicyr said. Him and Slasys picked
Wolfgang up and flew off toward the Iron Fist.
